room_title: Escape room "The Mission 2" by Wichita Room Escape in Wichita
room_description: Attention NEATO agents, we have discovered that our arch nemesis WAEDAAH has moved to Russia. Our intelligence suggests that they plan to set off three rockets somewhere in Russia. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to infiltrate WAEDAAH's headquarters and recover the rockets before they return. You have one hour. Good luck special agents!
